     RRmmaaiill interprets incoming mail received via uucp(1),  collapsing ``From''
     lines in the form generated by binmail(1) into a single line of the form
     ``return-path!sender'', and passing the processed mail on to sendmail(8).


     RRmmaaiill is explicitly designed for use with uucp and sendmail.

